Im not saying that its not true, just that nobody has ever posted any parses showing it to be true, while there are plenty of parses showing that 1200-1250 is indeed a cap on AC (in luclin). <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=solinarinnoruuk>Solinar Innoruuk</A> at: 12/6/02 7:50:52 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lyenaerz>Lyenae RZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 39<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/6/02 8:50:53 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2591.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: is there a new AC cap?</span><hr size=1> Solinar: Like you are doing any better?<br>
